xt_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158315;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158315";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:240:"Jay stays close to Crystal, moving slowly but confidently along, using the cart attached to her in order to keep herself steady. She has no idea what&#039;s going on.[br][br]Pepper stays close to Jay, protective but also still pretty happy.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418861772";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188617800";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158349;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158349";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:450:"/me keeps a wing draped over Jay. Her wings are notably larger than her Equestrian counterpart, and are actually proportionate to her body. Before long a rather large, strong looking buffalo approaches the two. He was carrying what looked to be the heaviest load of the cortege. Mainly formidable looking boxes covered in sheets. On the very top of the pile was a mattress and pillow. &quot;Hey! Jay, this is Al Bhed.&quot; The big buffalo just nods.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418862705";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188627628";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158351;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158351";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:170:"Jay stares at him in mild amazement. &quot;Is he gonna put that down?&quot; She asks, looking lazily toward Crystal. &quot;Or do I have to try and climb up there...&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418862972";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188629798";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158353;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158353";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:282:"/me giggles. &quot;Nope!&quot; She promptly scoops Pepper up and places her on the back of her neck where fur and feather meet, then, a moment later, scoops Jay up, sweeping her off her hooves. &quot;Up you go!&quot; She spread her wings and gave a strong flap to leave the ground. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418863225";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188632829";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158355;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158355";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:431:"Both Jay and Pepper react the same; fidgeting a little but not a lot, just kinda going through the motions as necessary in a calm, content way.[br]Both Jay and Pepper would then curl in against each other adorably. Pepper could sleep if Jay wants to. A simple mind is equally capable of just sitting around for a while.[br]Jay is clearly in no state for coherent conversation, and it&#039;s probably not the result of JUST alcohol.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418863462";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188634704";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158362;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158362";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScra